text: Stade Municipal de Berrechid () is a football-specific stadium in Berrechid, Morocco. It is the home stadium of Botola side CA Youssoufia Berrechid. The stadium has a capacity of 5,000.http://www.worldstadiums.com/africa/countries/morocco.shtml worldstadiums.com == References == Category:Football venues in Morocco
